msgid "Perspective"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user_manual/painting_with_assistants.rst:63
msgid "This ruler allows you to draw and manipulate grids on the canvas that can serve as perspective guides for your painting. A grid can be added to your canvas by first clicking the tool in the toolbar and then clicking four points on the canvas which will serve as the four corners of your grid."
