msgstr ""

#: ../../user_manual/painting_with_assistants.rst:70
msgid "The grid can be manipulated by pulling on any of its four corners. The grid can be extended by clicking and dragging a midpoint of one of its edges. This will allow you to expand the grid at other angles. This process can be repeated on any subsequent grid or grid section. If you press the :kbd:`Shift` key while holding any of the corner handles, they'll snap to one of the other corner handles, in sets. You can delete any grid by clicking on the cancel button at its center. This tool can be used to build reference for complex scenes."
msgstr ""

